# Kanon MCP Integration

Kanon MCP tools are available for project management. Use the installed skills:

- `/kanon-init` — Scan codebase, create project, seed issues and roadmap items
- `/kanon-create-issue` — Create an issue from natural language description
- kanon-mcp skill — Issue management, board updates, state transitions
- kanon-roadmap skill — Capture deferred work as roadmap items

When creating issues, follow these conventions:
- Title format: `[Area] Verb phrase` (e.g., `[API] Add authentication middleware`)
- Always check available groups before creating: call `kanon_list_groups(projectKey)`
- Assign groupKey when a matching group exists
